          "Learning in and through the arts prepares students for a life enriched through engagement in the creative process, an appreciation of aesthetics and an understanding of the relationships between the arts and society. Arts literacy enhances a student's communication, analytical thinking, problem solving and multi-cultural awareness. Adopted October 21, 2004."
